543
00:41:19,214 --> 00:41:21,091
Jako já?

544
00:41:21,091 --> 00:41:21,717
Cože?

545
00:41:29,142 --> 00:41:31,770
Co to děláš?

546
00:41:34,607 --> 00:41:35,858
Tohle?

547
00:41:35,983 --> 00:41:39,695
